projects to keep the momentum going?

00:56:38.719 --> 00:56:42.840
So one thing we do is we have, we have artifacts that people can share.

00:56:43.120 --> 00:56:46.479
People do share once every six to eight weeks, what are they working on?

00:56:47.080 --> 00:56:50.040
So, like I said, this is a forum for every team to come and every small team

